  ‚Äñ Define the ‚ù¨real matrix-vector product‚ù≠ $z$ of $A$ with $x$
    by $z_{i} = ‚àë_{j = 1}^{n} A_{ij}x_j$ ‚¶â

  ‚Äñ We denote the matrix vector product $z$ by $Ax$. ‚¶â
‚¶â

